title: Statler Brothers - Complete Lester 'Roadhog' Moran ...
description:
WEAK radio (1750 on your AM dial) presents Lester 'Roadhog' Moran and the Cadillac Cowboys; Red, Wesley and Wichita. The complete collection from the boys from Rainbow Valley, Virginia. Lester and the boys are the comedic alter-ego of The Statler Brothers. 

Tracks 1-6 are from the 1972 album 'Country Music Then and Now' (Mercury SR-61367). Tracks 7-21 are from the 1974 album 'Alive at the Johnny Mack Brown High School' (Mercury SRM1-708).

I downloaded this from somewhere, but don't remember where. It is 128Kbps which is fine for this album.

Please seed after you have completed the download.
